<h3 id="ca-2-2-control-enhancement-m-h">CA-2 (2) Control Enhancement (M) (H)</h3>
<p>The organization includes as part of security control assessments, [FedRAMP Assignment: at least annually], [Selection: announced; unannounced], [Selection (one or more): in-depth monitoring; vulnerability scanning; malicious user testing; insider threat assessment; performance/load testing; [Assignment: organization-defined other forms of security assessment]].<br />
<b>CA-2 (2) Additional FedRAMP Requirements and Guidance:</b><br />
<b>Requirement:</b> To include ‚Äòannounced‚Äô, ‚Äòvulnerability scanning‚Äô to occur at least annually.</p>

