<h3 id="ca-3-3-control-enhancement-m-h">CA-3 (3) Control Enhancement (M) (H)</h3>
<p>The organization prohibits the direct connection of an [Assignment: organization-defined unclassified, non-national security system] to an external network without the use of [FedRAMP Assignment: boundary protections which meet Trusted Internet Connection (TIC) requirements].<br />
<b>CA-3 (3) Additional FedRAMP Requirements and Guidance:</b><br />
<b>Guidance:</b> Refer to Appendix H ‚Äì Cloud Considerations of the TIC Reference Architecture document. Link: https://www.dhs.gov/publication/tic-reference-architecture-22</p>

